cast.overview: Susan Morrow receives a book manuscript from her ex-husband – a man she left 20 years earlier – asking for her opinion of his writing. As she reads, she is drawn into the fictional life of Tony Hastings, a mathematics professor whose family vacation turns violent.
cast.title: Nocturnal Animals

details.biography: Neil Jackson (born 5 March 1976) is a British stage, film and television actor, screen and song writer, and former amateur boxer, best known for his role as Marcus on "Blade: The Series", and as Sasha on the television series "Make It or Break It".
details.name: Neil Jackson
